1
00:00:00,020 --> 00:00:05,080
♪ Inside the state a city is built ♪

2
00:00:05,080 --> 00:00:10,190
♪ Where a benevolent emperor resides ♪

3
00:00:10,190 --> 00:00:15,330
♪ Court officials are brave and able ♪

4
00:00:15,330 --> 00:00:22,750
♪ The empress is fair ♪

5
00:00:25,580 --> 00:00:30,710
♪ Princes died too young to ascend the throne ♪

6
00:00:30,710 --> 00:00:35,570
♪ Princesses are spoiled and fragile ♪

7
00:00:35,840 --> 00:00:40,270
♪ Commoners are also the emperor’s children ♪

8
00:00:40,830 --> 00:00:49,630
♪ All are living peacefully ♪

9
00:00:49,930 --> 00:00:54,280
♪ Wish I could live a day for myself ♪

10
00:00:55,000 --> 00:00:59,380
♪ Follow my heart and ethics without distractions ♪

11
00:01:00,710 --> 00:01:03,400
♪ To be a good husband ♪

12
00:01:03,400 --> 00:01:05,970
♪ To be a caring father ♪

13
00:01:06,460 --> 00:01:10,110
♪ We were close when we first met ♪

14
00:01:10,460 --> 00:01:14,710
♪ I hope I can control my desires ♪

15
00:01:15,540 --> 00:01:20,060
♪ To be a worriless emperor and father ♪

16
00:01:21,120 --> 00:01:23,860
♪ Prudence tops all virtues ♪

17
00:01:23,860 --> 00:01:26,480
♪ People build the state ♪

18
00:01:26,750 --> 00:01:30,020
= Held in the Lonely Castle =
♪ May the world be peaceful ♪

19
00:01:30,020 --> 00:01:33,020
= Episode 13 =

20
00:01:33,340 --> 00:01:34,700
Xinhe has been in the palace for 6 years,

21
00:01:35,460 --> 00:01:36,940
yet she’s still just a Lady of County.

22
00:01:38,340 --> 00:01:39,340
She deserves a higher title.

23
00:01:40,780 --> 00:01:41,700
Now Madam Miao

24
00:01:41,700 --> 00:01:43,420
is pregnant with your child.

25
00:01:44,460 --> 00:01:46,700
She made an undeniable contribution.

26
00:01:47,780 --> 00:01:49,300
Once the baby is born,

27
00:01:49,500 --> 00:01:51,340
she should be promoted accordingly.

28
00:01:52,380 --> 00:01:53,260
I think

29
00:01:54,060 --> 00:01:56,340
censors won’t raise any objection to it.

30
00:01:57,460 --> 00:01:58,860
I don’t want to wait till the baby is born.

31
00:01:59,860 --> 00:02:01,580
I am going to promote Xinhe
to Zhaoyi (a title of concubine)

32
00:02:02,060 --> 00:02:03,700
before the baby is born.

33
00:02:07,780 --> 00:02:08,500
Well…

34
00:02:09,860 --> 00:02:12,660
This never happened before

35
00:02:12,780 --> 00:02:14,900
to promote a Lady of County (a title of concubine)

36
00:02:15,340 --> 00:02:17,340
directly to Zhaoyi.

37
00:02:18,740 --> 00:02:20,300
Censors will stand against it.

38
00:02:21,460 --> 00:02:22,860
Xinhe has been in the palace for years.

39
00:02:23,620 --> 00:02:25,780
She is pure, kindhearted and gentle.

40
00:02:27,180 --> 00:02:28,140
After six years,

41
00:02:28,180 --> 00:02:29,500
she’s still a Lady of County.

42
00:02:29,860 --> 00:02:31,340
That is extremely unfair to her.

43
00:02:32,300 --> 00:02:33,140
Now

44
00:02:33,660 --> 00:02:35,660
she is pregnant with a royal child.

45
00:02:36,700 --> 00:02:38,460
It is already late for me

46
00:02:38,900 --> 00:02:39,980
to give her what she deserves.

47
00:02:41,980 --> 00:02:44,620
Madam Miao is not the only one
who hasn’t got promoted.

48
00:02:45,180 --> 00:02:46,340
In the past 5 years,

49
00:02:46,340 --> 00:02:49,100
no concubine has been promoted.

50
00:02:50,060 --> 00:02:51,340
There are three ladies of county

51
00:02:51,340 --> 00:02:52,980
who came to the palace earlier than Madam Miao.

52
00:02:54,700 --> 00:02:56,500
Xinhe is different from them.

53
00:02:56,980 --> 00:02:59,140
She is different in your heart,

54
00:02:59,740 --> 00:03:01,180
but to others,

55
00:03:01,460 --> 00:03:02,860
she is the same with the other

56
00:03:02,860 --> 00:03:03,940
three ladies of county.

57
00:03:04,860 --> 00:03:06,700
Everyone says you are close with her.

58
00:03:07,100 --> 00:03:08,660
Why don’t you trust her?

59
00:03:09,260 --> 00:03:10,060
Besides,

60
00:03:10,100 --> 00:03:11,220
even if she’s been promoted to a Consort

61
00:03:11,220 --> 00:03:12,300
rather than Zhaoyi,

62
00:03:12,500 --> 00:03:14,300
her child will still call you mother,

63
00:03:14,300 --> 00:03:15,260
and call her sister (the title that a concubine's
child used to call birth mother in Song).

64
00:03:32,020 --> 00:03:32,780
Danshu.

65
00:03:42,340 --> 00:03:44,180
After I became the Empress,

66
00:03:45,260 --> 00:03:46,660
I proposed to promote

67
00:03:47,100 --> 00:03:48,060
three ladies of county

68
00:03:48,060 --> 00:03:49,660
including Madam Miao

69
00:03:49,660 --> 00:03:50,580
in 1034 A.D.,

70
00:03:51,380 --> 00:03:53,140
and you approved.

71
00:03:53,740 --> 00:03:54,540
But

72
00:03:54,900 --> 00:03:56,180
censors objected it,

73
00:03:56,460 --> 00:03:57,860
saying concubines

74
00:03:57,980 --> 00:03:59,700
already enjoyed the offerings from the people

75
00:03:59,820 --> 00:04:00,980
and a luxurious life.

76
00:04:01,540 --> 00:04:02,660
Promotion out of no reason

77
00:04:02,980 --> 00:04:04,500
would only create arrogance.

78
00:04:05,260 --> 00:04:06,300
I was criticized

79
00:04:06,300 --> 00:04:08,540
for showing grace with public welfare.

80
00:04:14,140 --> 00:04:15,460
That was because the farce

81
00:04:15,540 --> 00:04:17,060
made by the former empress with
Lady Shang and Lady Yang

82
00:04:17,060 --> 00:04:19,100
caused unexpected turmoil at the court,

83
00:04:19,940 --> 00:04:21,340
and I just took the throne,

84
00:04:21,700 --> 00:04:23,060
I didn’t want to hear the court

85
00:04:23,060 --> 00:04:25,260
arguing about harem all day long.

86
00:04:26,660 --> 00:04:27,620
I did wrong to you.

87
00:04:29,020 --> 00:04:31,860
But this time, even if someone disagrees with it,

88
00:04:32,180 --> 00:04:33,300
you won’t be involved.

89
00:04:34,260 --> 00:04:36,060
It’s Lv Yijian’s proposal

90
00:04:37,180 --> 00:04:38,900
to promoted Xinhe to Zhaoyi immediately

91
00:04:39,500 --> 00:04:40,540
at the court in front of everyone.

92
00:04:42,580 --> 00:04:43,420
The Prime Minister Lv?

93
00:04:45,060 --> 00:04:46,620
It is an exception

94
00:04:46,820 --> 00:04:47,780
to promote Madam Miao to Zhaoyi.

95
00:04:49,860 --> 00:04:51,060
It is my idea.

96
00:04:51,820 --> 00:04:53,220
It won’t involve you.

97
00:05:04,260 --> 00:05:04,860
You…

98
00:05:05,420 --> 00:05:06,660
I have to say something

99
00:05:07,580 --> 00:05:08,780
to Your Majesty.

100
00:05:13,860 --> 00:05:14,540
Say it.

101
00:05:17,460 --> 00:05:19,580
My objection to the promotion

102
00:05:19,580 --> 00:05:22,020
before the royal baby is born

103
00:05:22,900 --> 00:05:25,300
is not because I’m afraid of
being criticized by censors,

104
00:05:26,060 --> 00:05:27,700
but because I consider it inappropriate.

105
00:05:28,340 --> 00:05:30,460
This is about the harem.

106
00:05:30,500 --> 00:05:32,700
So it is within my duty.

107
00:05:33,260 --> 00:05:34,500
I have to tell Your Majesty

108
00:05:34,500 --> 00:05:35,860
the reason

109
00:05:36,100 --> 00:05:37,020
of my objection.

110
00:05:40,460 --> 00:05:41,740
The thing happened in 1034 A.D.

111
00:05:43,340 --> 00:05:44,700
made me feel

112
00:05:46,100 --> 00:05:47,700
wronged,

113
00:05:50,300 --> 00:05:51,980
but then I realized I made three mistakes.

114
00:05:53,980 --> 00:05:54,740
First,

115
00:05:55,540 --> 00:05:57,180
at that time, I just took control of the harem.

116
00:05:57,540 --> 00:05:58,580
I did need support

117
00:05:59,340 --> 00:06:01,140
and had the intention of associating with concubines.

118
00:06:02,340 --> 00:06:03,580
My intention was not wrong.

119
00:06:04,780 --> 00:06:07,340
But I should let them see

120
00:06:07,660 --> 00:06:08,500
my sincerity and virtues

121
00:06:08,500 --> 00:06:09,700
in daily conversation

122
00:06:09,700 --> 00:06:11,820
and contact,

123
00:06:12,420 --> 00:06:13,740
instead of

124
00:06:14,260 --> 00:06:16,540
using the concubine positions which the court paid for

125
00:06:16,980 --> 00:06:18,740
to build up my reputation.

126
00:06:20,500 --> 00:06:22,380
This shows my wrong morality.

127
00:06:23,140 --> 00:06:23,860
Second,

128
00:06:24,580 --> 00:06:26,340
before the fight the former empress
had with two ladies

129
00:06:26,580 --> 00:06:28,060
caused turmoil at the court.

130
00:06:28,540 --> 00:06:30,260
Many officials were involved.

131
00:06:30,540 --> 00:06:31,260
From this,

132
00:06:31,380 --> 00:06:32,700
I should’ve realized

133
00:06:32,780 --> 00:06:33,900
things in the harem

134
00:06:34,300 --> 00:06:36,660
is not just Your Majesty’s family business.

135
00:06:37,380 --> 00:06:40,100
Officials are concerned with
the promotion and demotion of concubines

136
00:06:40,100 --> 00:06:41,500
just as the state affairs at the court.

137
00:06:43,300 --> 00:06:44,540
I wasn’t in the palace for long

138
00:06:45,420 --> 00:06:46,780
and didn’t understand the circumstance

139
00:06:47,300 --> 00:06:48,220
nor had any authority,

140
00:06:48,260 --> 00:06:50,140
yet I was so anxious to exercise my power.

141
00:06:50,540 --> 00:06:52,060
This shows my insufficient planning.

142
00:06:54,180 --> 00:06:54,900
Third,

143
00:06:55,900 --> 00:06:58,420
three ladies of county all stayed
in the palace for long

144
00:06:58,780 --> 00:07:00,020
with merits and cautiousness.

145
00:07:00,700 --> 00:07:02,940
It was not wrong to promote them.

146
00:07:04,340 --> 00:07:05,980
They didn’t ask for promotion.

147
00:07:06,820 --> 00:07:08,140
It was out of my intention

148
00:07:08,300 --> 00:07:10,140
and they accepted it without declinature,

149
00:07:10,140 --> 00:07:11,420
which is natural and normal.

150
00:07:14,220 --> 00:07:15,900
But officials were very strict with

151
00:07:16,980 --> 00:07:19,580
concubines because of the former empress.

152
00:07:20,180 --> 00:07:23,740
The three of them were questioned
about their morality

153
00:07:24,380 --> 00:07:26,140
and wronged because of my selfish motives

154
00:07:26,860 --> 00:07:28,940
and insufficient planning.

155
00:07:30,580 --> 00:07:32,660
That was what I felt most ashamed of.

156
00:07:36,620 --> 00:07:39,300
This shows my inadequate consideration.

157
00:08:54,820 --> 00:09:01,460
= The Silver Gate =

158
00:09:10,300 --> 00:09:12,220
That’s all about daily etiquettes and rules on duty

159
00:09:12,260 --> 00:09:13,220
for today.

160
00:09:14,180 --> 00:09:16,060
= Liang Quanyi =
Now let’s talk about the most important rules

161
00:09:16,260 --> 00:09:18,300
that can cost your life if you break them.

162
00:09:18,460 --> 00:09:20,860
I invited the Manager of the Inner East Gate

163
00:09:20,980 --> 00:09:22,380
Mr. Zhang Maoze

164
00:09:22,580 --> 00:09:24,060
to teach you.

165
00:09:24,540 --> 00:09:25,900
You must pay

166
00:09:25,900 --> 00:09:27,060
all your attention

167
00:09:27,100 --> 00:09:28,420
to his lecture.

168
00:09:30,980 --> 00:09:32,180
Please, Mr. Zhang.

169
00:09:32,380 --> 00:09:33,460
Thank you, Quanyi.

170
00:09:36,740 --> 00:09:39,420
I am the Manager of the Inner East Gate.

171
00:09:40,020 --> 00:09:41,340
Today I’m going to tell you

172
00:09:41,340 --> 00:09:42,940
the important rules related to

173
00:09:42,940 --> 00:09:44,580
the gate.

174
00:09:46,180 --> 00:09:47,220
First of all,

175
00:09:47,540 --> 00:09:49,660
what you always need to keep in mind is that

176
00:09:50,380 --> 00:09:52,740
all the gates of the palace

177
00:09:52,780 --> 00:09:53,940
must be closed after dark.

178
00:09:54,420 --> 00:09:56,620
No one can open before sunrise.

179
00:09:57,100 --> 00:09:58,300
If anyone wants to open gates

180
00:09:58,380 --> 00:10:00,220
at night for some emergencies,

181
00:10:00,540 --> 00:10:01,500
he must have

182
00:10:03,940 --> 00:10:05,140
the fish tally endorsed by His Majesty.

183
00:10:07,300 --> 00:10:08,740
Rouge.

184
00:10:11,980 --> 00:10:13,020
It’s packed.

185
00:10:13,100 --> 00:10:14,220
Here you are.

186
00:10:26,740 --> 00:10:28,300
We are not open till noon.

187
00:10:29,340 --> 00:10:30,100
Foster mother!

188
00:10:35,020 --> 00:10:35,980
= Liang Yuansheng =
Yuansheng!

189
00:10:36,620 --> 00:10:38,140
Yuansheng is back!

190
00:10:41,060 --> 00:10:41,940
Yuansheng!

191
00:10:42,460 --> 00:10:43,180
Foster Mother!

192
00:10:44,340 --> 00:10:45,660
You are back!

193
00:10:46,060 --> 00:10:47,780
= Landlady of the Restaurant of Breeze, Zhang Lihua =
I haven’t heard from you for so long

194
00:10:48,260 --> 00:10:49,820
that I thought something happened to you.

195
00:10:49,940 --> 00:10:50,660
No.

196
00:10:50,700 --> 00:10:51,420
Foster Mother,

197
00:10:51,460 --> 00:10:52,580
we did have some unexpected troubles

198
00:10:52,580 --> 00:10:54,260
in Dingzhou.

199
00:10:54,260 --> 00:10:55,460
But blessed by you,

200
00:10:55,540 --> 00:10:56,660
we were not robbed by thieves.

201
00:10:57,500 --> 00:10:58,460
The money for selling goods,

202
00:10:58,900 --> 00:11:00,060
raw lake salt you wanted,

203
00:11:00,140 --> 00:11:01,820
and the recipe

204
00:11:01,820 --> 00:11:02,700
of the grape wine in Dayuan,

205
00:11:02,700 --> 00:11:03,660
I’ve taken all of them back.

206
00:11:05,220 --> 00:11:06,140
Excellent!

207
00:11:07,100 --> 00:11:10,260
If the gatekeeper opened gate without verifying,

208
00:11:10,740 --> 00:11:13,020
with unmatched tally

209
00:11:13,380 --> 00:11:16,980
or tally without endorsement,

210
00:11:17,500 --> 00:11:19,780
he shall be severely punished according to the law.

211
00:11:23,340 --> 00:11:24,460
- Officer Ren. - Officer Ren.

212
00:11:29,860 --> 00:11:34,060
= Ren Shouzhong, courtesy name Jichen =

213
00:11:35,180 --> 00:11:36,300
Understood?

214
00:11:36,700 --> 00:11:38,940
Understood.

215
00:11:49,500 --> 00:11:50,380
What’s your name?

216
00:11:52,540 --> 00:11:54,340
Zheng, Zheng Ye.

217
00:11:56,540 --> 00:11:58,940
Repeat what Mr. Zhang said.

218
00:12:01,580 --> 00:12:02,220
Gate…

219
00:12:03,100 --> 00:12:05,540
Gates, gates should not be open

220
00:12:06,300 --> 00:12:09,380
after, after dark.

221
00:12:10,620 --> 00:12:12,860
I, if anyone wants to open the gate

222
00:12:13,460 --> 00:12:16,300
at night for some emergencies,

223
00:12:16,860 --> 00:12:17,820
he must have

224
00:12:18,660 --> 00:12:21,340
the fish tally endorsed by His Majesty.

225
00:12:21,980 --> 00:12:28,140
It should have the time and reason written on it.

226
00:12:28,420 --> 00:12:29,300
Enough!

227
00:12:30,420 --> 00:12:32,420
That’s completely a mess!

228
00:12:33,820 --> 00:12:35,380
If you can’t even remember a few lines,

229
00:12:35,460 --> 00:12:36,860
how can your work in the palace?

230
00:12:44,940 --> 00:12:45,820
Some of you

231
00:12:46,100 --> 00:12:47,620
will take the key

232
00:12:47,620 --> 00:12:49,180
to the gates of the palace.

233
00:12:50,340 --> 00:12:51,460
If you made any mistakes,

234
00:12:51,940 --> 00:12:53,380
you will lose your life for that.

235
00:12:56,700 --> 00:12:58,500
Officer Ren is not joking.

236
00:12:58,740 --> 00:12:59,820
Gatekeepers

237
00:12:59,820 --> 00:13:01,300
who let people in or out against the law

238
00:13:01,900 --> 00:13:02,820
shall be at least exiled

239
00:13:03,140 --> 00:13:05,260
or even hanged.

240
00:13:07,060 --> 00:13:07,900
You, go out

241
00:13:08,420 --> 00:13:09,740
and kneel to reflect on yourself.

242
00:13:10,500 --> 00:13:11,980
No dinner for you today.

243
00:13:30,060 --> 00:13:30,820
What about you?

244
00:13:31,900 --> 00:13:32,940
Did you remember everything?

245
00:13:34,500 --> 00:13:35,340
Yes.

246
00:13:36,220 --> 00:13:37,980
Repeat what Mr. Zhang just said.

247
00:13:38,900 --> 00:13:39,580
Yes, sir.

248
00:13:40,420 --> 00:13:42,260
Just now Mr. Zhang said

249
00:13:42,540 --> 00:13:44,180
all the gates of the palace

250
00:13:44,180 --> 00:13:45,220
shall be closed after dark.

251
00:13:45,420 --> 00:13:47,460
No one can open before sunrise.

252
00:13:47,780 --> 00:13:49,060
If anyone wants to open the gate

253
00:13:49,340 --> 00:13:50,900
at night for some emergencies,

254
00:13:51,260 --> 00:13:52,940
he must have the fish tally endorsed by His Majesty.

255
00:13:53,220 --> 00:13:55,340
He must write down the time

256
00:13:55,660 --> 00:13:56,660
and detailed reason,

257
00:13:56,900 --> 00:13:58,540
the gate that needs to open,

258
00:13:58,820 --> 00:14:01,140
the number and identity of people
who need to go in and out

259
00:14:01,540 --> 00:14:03,140
and send the information to the Cabinet.

260
00:14:04,540 --> 00:14:09,340
= Restaurant of Breeze, Closed =

261
00:14:09,340 --> 00:14:11,420
Yuansheng can come back safe and sound

262
00:14:11,740 --> 00:14:12,700
with the recipe

263
00:14:12,700 --> 00:14:13,860
of grape wine.

264
00:14:13,980 --> 00:14:15,140
What a blessing!

265
00:14:16,020 --> 00:14:17,740
Today, we

266
00:14:17,980 --> 00:14:19,460
just eat and drink

267
00:14:19,900 --> 00:14:21,460
to celebrate his return!

268
00:14:21,700 --> 00:14:22,340
Great!

269
00:14:22,420 --> 00:14:23,700
Yuansheng has helped a lot this time…

270
00:14:23,820 --> 00:14:24,460
Foster mother!

271
00:14:24,860 --> 00:14:27,060
- I just got a good son so easily.
- Foster mother,

272
00:14:27,060 --> 00:14:27,820
mother!

273
00:14:28,580 --> 00:14:29,460
Why don’t you go to take a shower

274
00:14:29,460 --> 00:14:30,300
and change clothes?

275
00:14:30,860 --> 00:14:32,860
I, I have to go to my uncle’s house now.

276
00:14:33,580 --> 00:14:35,020
Aren’t you going to rest a few days

277
00:14:35,140 --> 00:14:36,300
before you take your mom and

278
00:14:36,300 --> 00:14:37,180
your brother here?

279
00:14:37,300 --> 00:14:38,860
I’ve already arranged the rooms for you.

280
00:14:39,100 --> 00:14:40,060
This is the letter

281
00:14:40,100 --> 00:14:41,500
my brother Yuanheng sent to me.

282
00:14:42,540 --> 00:14:43,340
What happened?

283
00:14:43,900 --> 00:14:45,300
He said due to the pandemic,

284
00:14:45,700 --> 00:14:47,100
my uncle and mom were infected and critically ill.

285
00:14:48,020 --> 00:14:49,060
And there was no more news from him.

286
00:14:51,820 --> 00:14:53,740
The tally is carved with a shape of fish

287
00:14:53,740 --> 00:14:54,660
and the name of the gate.

288
00:14:54,900 --> 00:14:57,220
Every tally is divided into two parts.

289
00:14:57,540 --> 00:14:59,620
= Liang Yuanheng =
Gatekeepers and the guard leads of each gate hold

290
00:14:59,620 --> 00:15:00,580
one of the two parts.

291
00:15:00,900 --> 00:15:02,260
Before opening the gate,

292
00:15:02,460 --> 00:15:04,060
the gatekeeper

293
00:15:04,260 --> 00:15:06,300
needs to prepare the guards of the gate

294
00:15:06,660 --> 00:15:09,260
to line up on both sides of the gate,

295
00:15:09,500 --> 00:15:10,460
and light up the torch.

296
00:15:10,700 --> 00:15:14,140
Both the guard lead and the eunuch
need to check the tally

297
00:15:14,420 --> 00:15:15,540
and make sure nothing is wrong

298
00:15:15,540 --> 00:15:16,820
and then they can open the gate.

299
00:15:17,380 --> 00:15:18,420
Even if the tally does match,

300
00:15:18,620 --> 00:15:20,580
if the gatekeeper opened the door without verifying,

301
00:15:20,780 --> 00:15:22,580
with unmatched tally

302
00:15:22,740 --> 00:15:25,660
or tally without endorsement

303
00:15:25,780 --> 00:15:27,500
shall be severely punished according to the law.

304
00:15:32,340 --> 00:15:33,260
Every word is correct.

305
00:15:37,620 --> 00:15:38,780
What’s your name?

306
00:15:40,020 --> 00:15:40,900
Liang Yuanheng.

307
00:15:41,140 --> 00:15:42,700
Yuanheng from Yuan Heng Li Zhen
(Benevolence, courtesy, righteousness and integrity).

308
00:15:49,940 --> 00:15:50,740
Officer Ren.

309
00:15:52,020 --> 00:15:54,180
What a reckless bastard!

310
00:15:54,580 --> 00:15:56,180
How dare you say the name of His Majesty!

311
00:15:56,940 --> 00:15:57,700
Officer Ren,

312
00:15:57,820 --> 00:15:58,780
this kid

313
00:15:58,780 --> 00:15:59,940
should be 8 or 9 years old.

314
00:16:00,220 --> 00:16:01,020
Before he came here,

315
00:16:01,180 --> 00:16:02,500
his family must haven’t taught him well.

316
00:16:02,500 --> 00:16:03,540
A wild child

317
00:16:03,540 --> 00:16:04,820
who knows nothing about taboos.

318
00:16:04,940 --> 00:16:06,540
He seems literate,

319
00:16:06,900 --> 00:16:08,780
unlike an untaught kid.

320
00:16:11,420 --> 00:16:14,780
How old are you?

321
00:16:15,260 --> 00:16:16,380
Who do you have in your family?

322
00:16:17,140 --> 00:16:18,940
I... I...

323
00:16:19,140 --> 00:16:20,540
I am ten years old.

324
00:16:21,500 --> 00:16:22,980
I was born in 1027 A.D.

325
00:16:24,500 --> 00:16:28,020
I have no one left in my family.

326
00:16:29,020 --> 00:16:30,020
No one?

327
00:16:30,940 --> 00:16:31,740
What about your parents?

328
00:16:32,460 --> 00:16:33,140
My...

329
00:16:34,700 --> 00:16:36,420
my father died of an illness

330
00:16:36,660 --> 00:16:37,820
in the year of my birth.

331
00:16:38,660 --> 00:16:40,820
My mother took me

332
00:16:40,820 --> 00:16:42,020
to my uncle’s place in City Liao.

333
00:16:43,020 --> 00:16:43,820
Not long ago,

334
00:16:44,660 --> 00:16:46,180
there was an outbreak of pharyngitis in City Liao.

335
00:16:46,740 --> 00:16:48,180
My mother and uncle

336
00:16:48,820 --> 00:16:50,820
died from it.

337
00:16:52,300 --> 00:16:55,220
If you were just some naughty kid from rural area,

338
00:16:55,340 --> 00:16:56,820
it would just be a mistake to forget the taboo

339
00:16:56,860 --> 00:16:58,500
and earn yourself the cane.

340
00:16:58,540 --> 00:17:00,260
But now you are in the palace

341
00:17:00,420 --> 00:17:01,980
serving for the royals.

342
00:17:02,140 --> 00:17:04,180
Breaking the taboo will cost your life.

343
00:17:06,780 --> 00:17:07,500
Officer Ren,

344
00:17:08,540 --> 00:17:09,940
Madam Miao will deliver

345
00:17:10,220 --> 00:17:11,340
the baby soon.

346
00:17:17,340 --> 00:17:18,620
Imprison him first.

347
00:17:19,540 --> 00:17:21,060
I’ll look at the palace rules

348
00:17:21,540 --> 00:17:22,620
before I report this to Her Highness

349
00:17:22,620 --> 00:17:23,940
to see what punishment he should receive.

350
00:17:31,660 --> 00:17:32,420
= Restaurant of Breeze =
Yuansheng,

351
00:17:32,820 --> 00:17:34,020
send me a message

352
00:17:34,100 --> 00:17:35,220
about what happened

353
00:17:35,420 --> 00:17:36,380
once you reach your uncle’s home.

354
00:17:37,660 --> 00:17:39,660
If there’s anything we can help,

355
00:17:39,900 --> 00:17:40,940
just tell us,

356
00:17:41,540 --> 00:17:42,340
you hear me?

357
00:17:47,540 --> 00:17:49,700
You allowed me to go back to visit my mother

358
00:17:50,140 --> 00:17:51,860
and prepared horse and money for me in such a hurry.

359
00:17:52,380 --> 00:17:54,180
I don’t know how I can repay your kindness.

360
00:17:55,300 --> 00:17:57,740
I just wish my mother and uncle can recover,

361
00:17:58,540 --> 00:17:59,420
Yuanheng can stay safe and sound.

362
00:17:59,660 --> 00:18:00,820
Once I take them here,

363
00:18:01,500 --> 00:18:02,740
I’ll focus on

364
00:18:02,740 --> 00:18:04,300
the business

365
00:18:04,300 --> 00:18:05,020
from the Capital to Xixia.

366
00:18:08,740 --> 00:18:09,580
Go.

367
00:18:10,020 --> 00:18:10,940
Take care.

368
00:18:12,020 --> 00:18:12,660
Okay.

369
00:18:42,540 --> 00:18:43,500
Yuanheng,

370
00:18:44,220 --> 00:18:46,940
your uncle and mother were gone.

371
00:18:48,020 --> 00:18:49,620
Our family was poor.

372
00:18:50,460 --> 00:18:52,660
And now we own a huge debt

373
00:18:53,180 --> 00:18:54,940
for hiring a physician and the funeral.

374
00:18:56,060 --> 00:18:56,820
From now on,

375
00:18:57,820 --> 00:19:00,060
I can’t

376
00:19:00,060 --> 00:19:01,460
feed you anymore.

377
00:19:04,900 --> 00:19:06,460
You are so smart.

378
00:19:07,820 --> 00:19:09,140
I managed to

379
00:19:09,820 --> 00:19:11,340
find you a good job.

380
00:19:12,820 --> 00:19:14,020
You’ll work

381
00:19:14,100 --> 00:19:15,820
in the most glorious place in the world.

382
00:19:31,860 --> 00:19:32,500
Your Majesty,

383
00:19:33,300 --> 00:19:35,340
Madam Xu of Dangyang County came to the palace.

384
00:19:35,340 --> 00:19:36,220
She is at the door,

385
00:19:36,380 --> 00:19:37,580
asking if you have time

386
00:19:37,580 --> 00:19:38,900
to meet with her.

387
00:19:41,020 --> 00:19:42,180
Let her in.

388
00:19:53,540 --> 00:19:54,220
Madam,

389
00:19:57,700 --> 00:19:58,980
please, have a seat.

390
00:20:10,620 --> 00:20:12,260
You love me since I was a kid,

391
00:20:12,940 --> 00:20:15,300
and now I married Xinhe,

392
00:20:15,740 --> 00:20:17,380
you are literally

393
00:20:17,500 --> 00:20:18,500
the closest person to me.

394
00:20:20,300 --> 00:20:21,540
I don’t deserve it.

395
00:20:22,020 --> 00:20:23,820
Your Majesty, you really flatter me.

396
00:20:24,660 --> 00:20:26,540
= Zhao Zhen’s wet nurse, Madam Xu =

397
00:20:26,540 --> 00:20:27,300
Your Majesty,

398
00:20:28,220 --> 00:20:29,580
please have a look.

399
00:20:36,460 --> 00:20:38,100
Things on this list

400
00:20:38,300 --> 00:20:39,460
are all in my house.

401
00:20:40,340 --> 00:20:42,020
I’ve recorded all the gifts

402
00:20:42,220 --> 00:20:43,660
and people who sent them.

403
00:20:44,100 --> 00:20:45,140
In a few months,

404
00:20:45,620 --> 00:20:46,940
I couldn’t count how much I’ve received.

405
00:20:47,860 --> 00:20:49,300
I dare not to decide,

406
00:20:50,340 --> 00:20:53,140
so few days ago I listed everything

407
00:20:53,700 --> 00:20:55,300
and sent the list to the Pavilion of Phoenix

408
00:20:55,660 --> 00:20:56,780
to let Xinhe decide.

409
00:20:58,500 --> 00:21:01,020
Today Officer Ren picked me up to the palace,

410
00:21:01,460 --> 00:21:02,820
and I went to visit Xinhe first.

411
00:21:03,420 --> 00:21:04,340
She said

412
00:21:04,940 --> 00:21:06,780
she dares not to decide either.

413
00:21:07,420 --> 00:21:08,740
Everything depends on you.

414
00:21:10,380 --> 00:21:12,100
The box hasn’t been opened.

415
00:21:13,100 --> 00:21:14,820
Things in it haven’t been touched.

416
00:21:15,940 --> 00:21:17,540
She told me to send it to you,

417
00:21:18,380 --> 00:21:19,820
saying you will decide.

418
00:21:23,740 --> 00:21:25,060
You moved to the palace

419
00:21:25,300 --> 00:21:26,740
to accompany Xinhe.

420
00:21:29,060 --> 00:21:30,980
Officer Ren told me

421
00:21:31,540 --> 00:21:34,180
Her Highness asked him to make arrangement

422
00:21:34,180 --> 00:21:35,780
according to conventions and rules.

423
00:21:36,380 --> 00:21:37,780
It is required by the court,

424
00:21:38,460 --> 00:21:40,780
not because of the relationship.

425
00:21:47,580 --> 00:21:48,660
That is very kind of her.

426
00:22:00,100 --> 00:22:01,340
The Ministry of Internal Service

427
00:22:01,500 --> 00:22:04,060
has four vacant positions.

428
00:22:04,220 --> 00:22:05,020
The Pavilion of Phoenix

429
00:22:05,020 --> 00:22:06,340
asked for some clever servant.

430
00:22:07,020 --> 00:22:08,540
But look at

431
00:22:08,660 --> 00:22:09,940
those idiots!

432
00:22:10,700 --> 00:22:12,260
They are either stupid

433
00:22:12,260 --> 00:22:14,380
or short-sighted.

434
00:22:26,500 --> 00:22:27,420
From tomorrow,

435
00:22:27,460 --> 00:22:29,140
give them two extra hours of class.

436
00:22:29,620 --> 00:22:31,100
Test them every day.

437
00:22:31,180 --> 00:22:32,540
If they can’t pass, don’t give them food.

438
00:22:33,820 --> 00:22:35,780
Keep Liang Yuanheng confined.

439
00:22:36,420 --> 00:22:38,660
If it wasn’t to avoid bringing bad luck

440
00:22:39,100 --> 00:22:40,180
to Madam Miao,

441
00:22:40,460 --> 00:22:41,540
he would’ve been punished

442
00:22:41,540 --> 00:22:42,940
with 50 slashes at his back at least.

443
00:22:46,580 --> 00:22:48,620
I think, we should tell Her Highness

444
00:22:48,980 --> 00:22:50,300
and just send him out of the palace.

445
00:23:03,340 --> 00:23:06,260
= The Hall of Happiness and Tranquility =

446
00:23:06,260 --> 00:23:08,900
= Zhao Yanyu =

447
00:23:12,660 --> 00:23:14,140
= Liaozi =

448
00:23:14,140 --> 00:23:14,740
Your Majesty,

449
00:23:15,100 --> 00:23:17,220
for today’s kitchen, the Imperial Kitchen…

450
00:23:17,260 --> 00:23:18,580
She is so considerate and thoughtful.

451
00:23:19,340 --> 00:23:21,060
She has thought of everything for Xinhe.

452
00:23:23,380 --> 00:23:25,140
She wanted to take good care of her

453
00:23:26,660 --> 00:23:28,580
but not to let anyone think

454
00:23:28,820 --> 00:23:31,020
Xinhe is spoiled for being pregnant.

455
00:23:33,300 --> 00:23:34,540
She knows clearly

456
00:23:35,740 --> 00:23:37,620
officials wanted to

457
00:23:38,020 --> 00:23:40,180
collude with the family with royal baby.

458
00:23:41,620 --> 00:23:43,060
So she told me to be cautious.

459
00:23:45,260 --> 00:23:46,500
Yet I blamed her.

460
00:24:19,860 --> 00:24:22,700
I have my body relying on the nourishment of

461
00:24:22,940 --> 00:24:26,340
the Yin and Yang of the world;

462
00:24:26,580 --> 00:24:28,260
I grew up in a nest built by a loving mother

463
00:24:28,340 --> 00:24:30,300
relying on the trees planted by my master.

464
00:24:33,140 --> 00:24:33,900
Your Majesty,

465
00:24:38,420 --> 00:24:41,060
Fan Xiwen wrote a good article indeed.

466
00:24:41,300 --> 00:24:43,180
He made excellent and impressive metaphors
and sarcasms.

467
00:24:43,780 --> 00:24:47,700
But does he really have to use

468
00:24:47,700 --> 00:24:49,300
this ugly and fat bird with unpleasant sound

469
00:24:49,740 --> 00:24:50,860
to reason?

470
00:24:51,820 --> 00:24:53,900
That bird is the noise at dawn.

471
00:24:54,380 --> 00:24:56,260
Why can’t he use some better-looking birds

472
00:24:56,260 --> 00:24:57,140
in his article?

473
00:24:58,100 --> 00:25:00,020
He used raven to express his feelings,

474
00:25:00,460 --> 00:25:02,500
so his fellows raised ravens

475
00:25:03,220 --> 00:25:05,980
to express their depression

476
00:25:06,140 --> 00:25:08,100
for their unadopted but sincere advice.

477
00:25:15,140 --> 00:25:16,500
Aren’t you worried

478
00:25:16,780 --> 00:25:17,740
ravens from the whole palace

479
00:25:17,740 --> 00:25:19,220
and even the whole capital

480
00:25:19,220 --> 00:25:20,060
hear the news

481
00:25:20,060 --> 00:25:21,580
and fly to the Hall of Peace?

482
00:25:22,340 --> 00:25:23,580
Your hall will be covered

483
00:25:24,140 --> 00:25:25,700
with black ravens.

484
00:25:26,100 --> 00:25:27,340
At every down

485
00:25:27,580 --> 00:25:28,740
they would nag at you at the same time,

486
00:25:29,220 --> 00:25:32,740
So how can a sword be a sharp weapon
if curls once used?

487
00:25:33,140 --> 00:25:35,660
How can a stone be a jade if changes once burned?

488
00:25:36,340 --> 00:25:39,180
I’d rather die to be heard than live voicelessly.

489
00:25:39,700 --> 00:25:42,420
I’d rather die to be heard than live voicelessly”

490
00:25:42,420 --> 00:25:43,380
Your Majesty.

491
00:25:46,900 --> 00:25:49,260
You are more sarcastic than

492
00:25:49,260 --> 00:25:50,220
Sun Fu, Ouyang Xiu and Cai Xiang.

493
00:25:52,860 --> 00:25:53,820
Alright,

494
00:25:54,140 --> 00:25:55,500
I am an old raven

495
00:25:55,540 --> 00:25:57,900
who nags all day long at you.

496
00:25:59,220 --> 00:26:01,100
Then you might as well make a slingshot

497
00:26:01,220 --> 00:26:03,100
and shoot the ugly raven away.

498
00:26:06,500 --> 00:26:07,340
Do you have any wine

499
00:26:08,100 --> 00:26:08,940
you made?

500
00:26:10,940 --> 00:26:12,820
Moyao (name of the wine) still takes a few more days.

501
00:26:13,100 --> 00:26:14,420
But I still have some Yingyu (name of the wine) left.

502
00:26:16,140 --> 00:26:18,460
Today I’ll want some wine from you

503
00:26:19,020 --> 00:26:20,140
to tell you an old thing

504
00:26:20,460 --> 00:26:21,860
that happened in 1027A.D.

505
00:26:42,620 --> 00:26:43,700
Don’t forget to send some food and clean water

506
00:26:43,700 --> 00:26:44,860
to this kid every day.

507
00:26:46,220 --> 00:26:47,100
I’ll try to ask Her Highness

508
00:26:48,260 --> 00:26:50,900
to show him some mercy.

509
00:26:52,740 --> 00:26:53,460
Okay.

510
00:27:13,260 --> 00:27:16,100
I made half way there but then came back.

511
00:27:18,100 --> 00:27:19,140
In the end, I still didn’t see

512
00:27:19,140 --> 00:27:20,460
my birth mother.

513
00:27:23,900 --> 00:27:24,900
The wet nurse said

514
00:27:25,340 --> 00:27:26,980
she felt relieved

515
00:27:28,020 --> 00:27:29,180
hearing Mr. Yan went there,

516
00:27:30,260 --> 00:27:31,340
but sad too,

517
00:27:33,700 --> 00:27:35,580
thinking that if he didn’t come in time,

518
00:27:37,780 --> 00:27:39,220
I could at least have a chance

519
00:27:40,340 --> 00:27:41,660
to see her in my life,

520
00:27:43,620 --> 00:27:45,060
to call her mother.

521
00:27:56,660 --> 00:27:57,740
It’s not.

522
00:27:58,420 --> 00:27:59,620
It’s not because of him.

523
00:28:01,740 --> 00:28:02,740
Actually Mr. Yan

524
00:28:03,740 --> 00:28:05,380
didn’t change my mind.

525
00:28:06,820 --> 00:28:08,380
He just gave me a reason

526
00:28:10,580 --> 00:28:12,260
for being cruel

527
00:28:14,220 --> 00:28:15,460
and unfilial.

528
00:28:19,380 --> 00:28:21,500
She hadn’t told you

529
00:28:22,540 --> 00:28:24,060
a single word

530
00:28:26,020 --> 00:28:27,060
or even showed you

531
00:28:27,060 --> 00:28:28,540
a little bit love,

532
00:28:28,900 --> 00:28:30,140
was she being cruel?

533
00:28:32,620 --> 00:28:34,100
She was not.

534
00:28:37,220 --> 00:28:38,860
It’s because she loved you so much.

535
00:28:41,700 --> 00:28:42,820
If you really

536
00:28:43,620 --> 00:28:45,900
went to the Mausoleum and called her mother,

537
00:28:47,420 --> 00:28:48,980
it would’ve ruined

538
00:28:49,940 --> 00:28:51,220
all the sacrifice she made

539
00:28:51,220 --> 00:28:52,220
for years.

540
00:29:04,740 --> 00:29:06,260
All the willful things I did later

541
00:29:09,980 --> 00:29:10,820
indeed…

542
00:29:28,180 --> 00:29:29,180
In 1034 A.D.,

543
00:29:32,340 --> 00:29:34,100
when you were blamed for

544
00:29:35,820 --> 00:29:38,620
showing grace with public welfare by censors,

545
00:29:40,500 --> 00:29:41,980
you were only in the palace
for less than half a year.

546
00:29:45,100 --> 00:29:46,180
You were only 19 years old,

547
00:29:47,020 --> 00:29:48,700
yet you already understood what an empress means.

548
00:29:49,460 --> 00:29:50,340
Since then,

549
00:29:51,180 --> 00:29:52,260
you’ve been cautious and self-restrained

550
00:29:53,260 --> 00:29:55,140
but never gone out of your way to curry favor.

551
00:29:59,500 --> 00:30:01,860
I don’t deserve it, Your Majesty.

552
00:30:06,940 --> 00:30:07,660
Come here,

553
00:30:18,620 --> 00:30:19,460
Danshu.

554
00:30:20,940 --> 00:30:21,620
This time,

555
00:30:22,820 --> 00:30:25,020
I must give Xinhe

556
00:30:25,300 --> 00:30:26,220
the title

557
00:30:26,220 --> 00:30:27,660
before the baby’s born.

558
00:30:32,220 --> 00:30:33,660
I understand your intention

559
00:30:33,740 --> 00:30:35,660
and your worries.

560
00:30:36,820 --> 00:30:39,620
Censors are worried that she’ll

561
00:30:39,620 --> 00:30:41,900
use my love and the child

562
00:30:42,940 --> 00:30:44,780
to earn more power and bewitch me,

563
00:30:45,660 --> 00:30:47,300
to collude with officials and disturb the court.

564
00:30:48,540 --> 00:30:50,060
But I’m her husband,

565
00:30:50,420 --> 00:30:51,700
